ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Burma) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (BURMA) REGULATIONS in order to add thirteen (13) individuals and three (3) entities to the Schedule of the Regulations, prohibiting them from transacting business with individuals and businesses in Canada, and freezing their assets unless otherwise authorized by the Minister of the Foreign Affairs.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0082 Publication Date: 2025-03-26
